{
  "stem": "142.6",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 79,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And when it was OK for us to come in, they will open the door.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, but I think Shlomo once was up there helping the SS.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I tried to stay out as much as I could from the-- from the eyes of the Germans.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I don't think I could survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because my main game at that point, that I knew that my days were numbered, is to be able to get the-- not get the attention of the Germans, but for me to be in a-- in a way out of them, to be for the next day and the next day and the next day.",
      "word_count": 56
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Like I told you before, you know, that war is going to end one day.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "It couldn't be forever.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And when that ends, I'd like to be alive and be able to-- to tell the story, which I was happy to do.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh it's always successful because they just waited 30 minutes.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They knew that it takes from 2 to 5 minutes, depending where they are.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "There's no-- and they're through, you know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So they waited-- they way 30 minutes to be able to open the doors and put the ventilation on so we can go and do our job.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They were screaming yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah, they were.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A lot of crying, a lot of, you know-- could you imagine, you are with all your family there, and you know you are dying?",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You know, it just doesn't take too long.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's why if you knew somebody, we tell them, you go there, where it's two minutes.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "In two minutes you are gone.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "If not, you go to the five minutes, you are going to three minutes of suffering is a big deal.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Could you imagine that?",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
